	<RoyalTitleDef ParentName="SWGCWTitle_ZsinjPrivateer_base">
		<defName>SWGCWTitle_ZsinjPrivateer_warlord</defName>
		<label>Warlord</label>
		<description>Zsinj's subordinate 'warlords' are those whom he has deemed exemplary in capability and loyalty, and can be entrusted with directing military campaigns on the galactic scale. These individuals are permitted to rule their holdings as lesser kings unto themselves, provided their devotion to Zsinj is not a matter of question. The individual receiving this title is likely the first to have this honor bestowed upon them, as Zsinj has not granted this title to any of his other top officers. This position ranks above any "flag officer" role, and as such the lesser admirals and generals under Zsinj's banner have no authority to challenge someone he has named a warlord.\n\nWarlords are trusted with the deployment of Zsinj's many Star Destroyers, and with the legions of his elite Raptor Corps. They are permitted to rule their held territories as an autonomous fiefdom, so long as they continue to contribute to Zsinj's military interests.</description>
